									=09
         Piston Top volume&nbsp; +&nbsp; Combustion chamber volume</b></td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td align=3D"right" nowrap=3D"nowrap" valign=3D"top"><b>Uncompress=
ed Volume&nbsp; =3D</b></td>
									<td nowrap=3D"nowrap" valign=3D"top"><b>Compressed Volume&nbsp; +&=
nbsp; Displacement</b></td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td align=3D"right" nowrap=3D"nowrap" valign=3D"top"><b>Compressio=
n Ratio&nbsp; =3D</b></td>
									<td nowrap=3D"nowrap" valign=3D"top"><b>Uncompressed volume&nbsp; =
=F7&nbsp; Compressed volume</b></td>
								</tr>
							</tbody></table>
						</div>
